.SH FIELDS
.TP
\f[B]retention.findings_days\f[R], \f[B]retention.evidence_days\f[R], \f[B]retention.runs_days\f[R]
Per\-class retention.
Evidence additionally follows a \f[I]keep\-if\-referenced\f[R] rule: a
row is never deleted while a finding still references it.
.TP
\f[B]evidence.max_payload_bytes\f[R] (default \f[B]16384\f[R])
Truncation ceiling for captured payloads.
When truncated, \f[B]evidence.original_sha256\f[R] is populated with the
SHA\-256 of the full body.
.PP
\f[B]scanner.max_concurrent_targets\f[R] (default \f[B]100\f[R])
