Concurrency caps.
.TP
\f[B]log.level\f[R] (default \f[B]info\f[R]), \f[B]log.output\f[R] (default \f[B]stderr\f[R])
Log level and sink.
.TP
\f[B]shutdown.drain_timeout\f[R] (default \f[B]10s\f[R])
Graceful drain window before forced exit.
.TP
\f[B]doctor.ntp_server\f[R]
